<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Fortitude" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Fortitude,</orth> 1) constancy, firmness of mind: <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.154" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 154</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.388" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 388</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 4.3.94" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 3, 94</bibl>.<lb />2) vigour, force, strength: <cit><quote>despairing of his own arm's f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.1.17" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 1, 17</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the f. of the place is best known to you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 1.3.222" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 3, 222</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>